        "timestamp": "2017-09-22 13:28:58.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 5: Code-Review-1\n\nThe sdnc_ip param defined in demo/heat/vCPE/vbrgemu/base_vcpe_vbrgemu_rackspace.yaml is never used. It is not visible inside the VM. To do so, you need to add the following instruction somewhere under # Create config files:\n\necho \"__sdnc_ip__\" > /opt/config/sdnc_ip.txt  (you can choose the filename that you like)\n\nAlso, you need to modify demo/heat/vCPE/vbrgemu/base_vcpe_vbrgemu_rackspace.env with the parameter value, for example:\nsdnc_ip: 10.0.7.1\n\nIf you don’t need to pass sdnc_ip parameter to the VM, you can simply remove the instructions from demo/heat/vCPE/vbrgemu/base_vcpe_vbrgemu_rackspace.yaml",
        "patchset_number": 5
      },
